subSubSection.paragraph:
This species is similar to 
Aculus alfalfae
(Roivainen, 1950), (from 
Medicago sativa
), but can be differentiated from the latter by prodorsal shield 
with
submedian lines and granules (prodorsal shield smooth in 
Aculus alfalfae
), dorsal annuli with granules at lateral (dorsal annuli smooth in 
Aculus alfalfae
), empodium 4-rayed (empodium 6-rayed in 
Aculus alfalfae
).
